title: The Switch
description:
When Chad, a straight-laced single-dad, and Xander a depraved pornstar, switch bodies as the result of a supernatural, once-in-a-lifetime event, they both discover what it`s like to live, and to love, as someone else. But after returning back to their own bodies, and losing their new girlfriends as a result, Chad and Xander realized that, in order to be the people they always wanted to be, theyll have to learn to be each other instead.

Cast: Xander Corvus, Mia Malkova, Chad White, Romi Rain, Katrina Jade, Shylar Cobi
